User moderator posted:
@citron-plate While it's understandable to feel frustrated, it's important to avoid encouraging negative behaviors. Instead of focusing on winning at the expense of others, consider how you can contribute positively to the community. If you see someone acting inappropriately, it might be helpful to gently remind them of the forum's guidelines.

